{"tid":2347873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"地產界批評「政治凌駕商業」","createTime":"2020-12-31T10:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T11:39:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d97cf5895dafb7be48b9676ad23012d7f1ad6648","tid":2347873,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:47:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/XIL7LYRTAFBUNN76W5WF2JYA2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FXIL7LYRTAFBUNN76W5WF2JYA2M%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=d2572a04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FXIL7LYRTAFBUNN76W5WF2JYA2M%2F&h=6a68cbe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/XIL7LYRTAFBUNN76W5WF2JYA2M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n地產界批評「政治凌駕商業」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bLh-832kFesY1EOUtTMck1iu_Bg=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/457RTM2RYNCXFOPTSUQY55YWJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbLh-832kFesY1EOUtTMck1iu_Bg%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F457RTM2RYNCXFOPTSUQY55YWJU.jpg&h=02ca56e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蘇振顯指過往從未聽聞因外交問題導致土地或物業買賣告吹個案，相信此次為首例。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】恒隆購入美國駐港總領事館的壽山村道項目，原本僅是一單普通商業交易，惟因為美方放售時正值香港訂立國安法、中美關係跌至新低，遭中方選擇強行阻止交易。有學者及測量師批評中方擾亂市場秩序，令政治凌駕香港商業行為。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：北京阻美領館賣港物業  買家恒隆：涉外交事務 專家：如凍結資產<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n德法領館售物業未遇阻<br />\n<br />\n回顧過往，不少外國領事館在港購置及放售物業，未曾出現同類事件。1997年，德國出售山頂歌賦山道的駐港領事官邸，獲電訊盈科主席李澤楷以3.9億元高價購入。另外，法國曾以山頂普樂道8號物業作為駐港總領事大屋，2011年以5.8億元向菱電發展出售；上述兩單交易都未受政治阻撓。<br />\n<br />\n蘇振顯測量師行董事總經理蘇振顯表示，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n經濟學家羅家聰指，中共向來選擇性執法，現時連涉及外國政府的商業行為都出現差別對待，料打擊外資信心，因外資最怕制度的不可預測，憂慮政權不跟既定法律和規矩做事，「唔會距離（撤資階段）好遠」。<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉雄則指，。。。。。。。。。直言「唔敢認同香港仲係一個自由市場」。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"cff58d55d19a93903239e52944282b8f3ae3b8f9","tid":2347873,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"哦，你已經犯咗國安法，人嚟，凍結資產同收監！"},{"pid":"11449e77162c37e88e45fa6f32d69ff25125c639","tid":2347873,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:49:47.000Z","msg":"林鄭算廢了， 睇下中共點對商界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4b7f0731c7e55cbd762da52b2c30495a083d7d","tid":2347873,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:50:46.000Z","msg":"地產遲早死"},{"pid":"48f194d800867085e83daeda6d795adc7ac027f2","tid":2347873,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"再嘈徵晒你啲地做國安用途，唔賠償"},{"pid":"6b45167c4beb1922e6f7893fe041f1cfd92612b7","tid":2347873,"uid":110080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:55:49.000Z","msg":"呢單都幾癲 地產商都中招"},{"pid":"f22f96fafb6fa48e7e6063bfd674371c5856894c","tid":2347873,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1316615eb97c80418d52ccf3c461d97913a0756c","tid":2347873,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3c8a52daecf77ce2c2e21bc5dc72f2c945dad176","tid":2347873,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:58:55.000Z","msg":"呢個乜水咁串國安都敢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d00e590aab1101aa270f724468a854b07c4fc2d","tid":2347873,"uid":117689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b45167c4beb1922e6f7893fe041f1cfd92612b7","tid":2347873,"uid":110080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:55:49.000Z","msg":"呢單都幾癲 地產商都中招"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"